RequestBody.content: How many medals did the USA win in the 2024 summer olympics?

text.value: How many medals did the USA win in the 2024 summer olympics?
The United States won a total of 126 medals at the 2024 Summer Olympics, which included 40 gold medals, 44 silver medals, and 42 bronze medals【3:0†source】.
